[BID 6N] Counting the keycards, the trump queen, and that diamond king, partner places the hand in 6NT.
[show NESW]Partner added up the keycards, the trump queen, and that diamond king and placed the hand in six notrump, which brought home all thirteen tricks. Answering each ask exactly, rather than guessing, is what lets the strong hand count the slam instead of gambling on it.}
